{"tid":704081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"灌醉酒促女撿屍　見她狂吐慾火全消偷錢走人","createTime":"2018-06-16T07:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T09:01:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb437a51f0f2c0c9cd273e97514f595bf34ac0c","tid":704081,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"廚師阿東（化名）覬覦酒促女子小可（化名）美貌，尾牙趁機灌醉她，帶去摩鐵欲性侵害，最後因小可不斷嘔吐，讓他慾火全消，偷走她皮包500元離去。台中地院依乘機性交未遂罪判刑2年；另依竊盜罪判處拘役40日。<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，判決指出，燒肉店廚師阿東結識店內酒促小可，105年1月24日晚間，阿東等人參加該店尾牙。席間阿東及在場員工不斷對小可勸酒，小可不勝酒力醉倒。<br />\n阿東叫車將她載往摩鐵。小可不斷嘔吐，阿東將她的衣物褪去、撕裂她的長裙，將她帶往浴缸浸泡清洗。小可在浴缸內嘔吐，阿東慾火全消，將她安頓後，竊取她皮包內500元離去。小可酒醒後報警。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/152330_0a6590197a456b5dfcec593d46b46a8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F152330_0a6590197a456b5dfcec593d46b46a8c.png&h=216d516f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180616/1374343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180616%2F1374343&d=Xss1rbCGGQoh133a3dErLP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bc590081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180616%2F1374343&h=c2d3abb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180616/1374343</a>"},{"pid":"744fc91bbe9fd0f651200593c6acecf6ee362e64","tid":704081,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"所亂"},{"pid":"6269ab9be6962ee9c6a5ba89dfd87a715037cfe7","tid":704081,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"都抽哂水啦"},{"pid":"556c403100849cea4536752c2a1f964693bf6253","tid":704081,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"744fc91bbe9fd0f651200593c6acecf6ee362e64","tid":704081,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dis